dct_description_sm: Map shows populated areas and settlements, buildings, landmarks, churches, mosques, synagogues, schools, hospitals, embassies, roads, railways, bridges, tunnels, boundaries, powerlines, prominent walls and fences, vegetation, and water features. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Includes location map, index to streets, glossary, and guide to numbered features. "Map information as of 1993." "WGS 84." "Grid--1,000 meter UTM zone 34." "Printed by DMA 7-95." "This sheet falls within NK 34-02 and NL 34-11, 1501A 1:250,000 and 3183 II and 3182 I, M709, 1:50,000." "Where street names cannot be shown on the graphic, the streets are identified by numbers."
